{"tid":814484,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"<<首爾攻略>> 求屌求狠批","createTime":"2018-09-11T09:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T07:24:35.000Z","uid":36502,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c9a21ef0726bf113f6969d6b38ff5a37f8bafc23","tid":814484,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/172328_0c6b4e6ddba9159af9d5ac0be7a68a70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F172328_0c6b4e6ddba9159af9d5ac0be7a68a70.jpg&h=c97e48fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同女朋友去，<br />\n做左成個星期功課，寫左呢個行程，求狠批<br />\n<br />\n第1日<br />\n主要係去市集：弘大自由市場➜ 食Road Steak ➜ 清溪廣場季節市集 ➜ 青春跑道市集 ➜ 食陳玉華奶奶元祖一隻雞 ➜ DP 青春跑道市集<br />\n<br />\n第2日<br />\n景福宮 ➜ 三清洞麵疙瘩 ➜ 北村韓屋村 ➜ 明洞樂天超市 ➜ 老媽的家豆腐鍋 ➜ 首爾塔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第3日<br />\n首爾大公園 ➜ 明洞食燒肉 ➜ 東大門市場<br />\n<br />\n第4日<br />\n食完阿峴洞醬蟹 ➜梨大 ➜ 新村➜春川炒辣雞➜ 弘大<br />\n<br />\n第5日<br />\n麻浦水產海鮮➜天空公園➜4點機"},{"pid":"b65baa38da26bef8b6fe92dd1f268f855ad273f1","tid":814484,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"諗緊 麻浦水產海鮮➜天空公園➜景福宮 ➜ 三清洞麵疙瘩 ➜ 北村韓屋村➜明洞食老媽的家豆腐鍋➜首爾塔<br />\n<br />\n咁樣GROUP埋一日夠唔夠時間"},{"pid":"6c12f984963844e646041afb510b6e76b2d93735","tid":814484,"uid":147233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:48:20.000Z","msg":"留名學野 十一月去"},{"pid":"62023a6796c1e140580130f300955a4a6ec2f4d6","tid":814484,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb3c1ad3c95bca1080754a8e3b8772c8068b839","tid":814484,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62023a6796c1e140580130f300955a4a6ec2f4d6","tid":814484,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T10:22:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr